# WooCommerce Hooks

## Product Page Hooks
- `woocommerce_before_single_product` - Before product content
- `woocommerce_single_product_summary` - Modify product summary (priority matters: 5=title, 10=price, 20=excerpt)
- `woocommerce_after_single_product_summary` - After summary (tabs, related products)
- `woocommerce_product_tabs` - Filter to add/remove/modify tabs

## Shop/Archive Hooks
- `woocommerce_before_shop_loop` - Before product grid
- `woocommerce_after_shop_loop` - After product grid
- `loop_shop_per_page` - Filter to change products per page
- `loop_shop_columns` - Filter to change grid columns

## Cart Hooks
- `woocommerce_before_cart` - Before cart table
- `woocommerce_add_to_cart_validation` - Validate before adding to cart
- `woocommerce_cart_item_price` - Filter individual cart item price display

## Checkout Hooks
- `woocommerce_checkout_fields` - Modify checkout form fields
- `woocommerce_checkout_process` - Validate checkout fields
- `woocommerce_checkout_update_order_meta` - Save custom field data to order
- `woocommerce_thankyou` - Order received page

**Priority Matters**: Always check existing hook priorities to place your actions in the right order
